Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9141aa2f26deeef4bc321e2a2305221406b734b","tid":2365987,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9ab9fd916ed0f84f5b72f92566e0c26d47588c4","tid":2365987,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9141aa2f26deeef4bc321e2a2305221406b734b","tid":2365987,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:40:20.000Z","msg":"你去？"},{"pid":"3aa944a1eb400916bbc819ccb751ebb97c34e983","tid":2365987,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d5fd8657c10802ed148b0b9735f1440893b780","tid":2365987,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:37:00.000Z","msg":"Block樓上先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83cfaa5c1dde94a580605baa4e22f2f3589b13a","tid":2365987,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:37:56.000Z","msg":"12港人越邊境案，未成年的廖子文及黃臨福早前獲內地釋放並移交本港。其中被控串謀縱火罪的廖子文完成14天檢疫隔離，今午到區域法院應訊。控方今申請修改控罪，改控一項串謀意圖危害生命而縱火罪，以及一項管有物品意圖摧毁或損壞財產的交替控罪，案件押後再訊。廖子文今出庭時神情輕鬆。他沒有申請保釋，離庭前向旁聽人士揮手。<br />\n<br />\n戴上黃色口罩的王婆婆今日原本帶著「Save 12」字樣的燈牌，打算入庭聲援；但經司法機構職員多次勸喻後，王婆婆同意將燈牌收起。<br />\n<br />\n廖子文今出庭時精神不錯，甫步出犯人欄即望向旁聽席，聽書記讀出控罪時亦大聲回答表示「清楚」。當他準備返回囚室時，向旁聽席揮手，更戚眉數次，似有笑意，神情輕鬆。辯方大律師其後在庭外指廖的精神及身體狀況均良好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210114/EABU4V5KQZHFLAM5W5MIOE4L3M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210114%2FEABU4V5KQZHFLAM5W5MIOE4L3M%2F&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuPE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=5c427dae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210114%2FEABU4V5KQZHFLAM5W5MIOE4L3M%2F&h=1b4584e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210114/EABU4V5KQZHFLAM5W5MIOE4L3M/</a>"},{"pid":"04d54366f29b8948042f3ff0b4cb5b6966c1aebc","tid":2365987,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4421fb0cc540cc61a31810c7dbcc382973fc75ca","tid":2365987,"uid":103965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a86a3487bf4d8fb3e9504cc9d61c11a2589a0c","tid":2365987,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23198ddc0e78aaed31e69f1ff7da614780888243","tid":2365987,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}